oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Statler Brothers Heads
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Statler Brothers;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color card (black on white) featuring silhouettes of the Statler Brothers's heads. This is probably a proof for a metal photoplate. On the back of the photo, a typed note says, "Statler Brothers November 1981." To view a poster that features the metal photoplate, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/21783
